section.section:
The agreement shall:
State the name and post office address of each party;
Identify the prior agreement to which it relates;
Describe the goods;
Describe any security interest or collateral security which was reserved or taken to secure the prior agreement and which is retained to secure the renewal, extension, or refund; and
State the amount of the extended principal, the agreed rate of charge, the number of scheduled installments, and the time and amount of each installment.
